WESTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SOUTH CAROLINA.
23 FOOT VESSEL, WHITE HULL, THREE PERSONS ON BOARD,
OVERDUE GEORGETOWN (34-22.0N 079-17.6W) TO
THREE MILE REEF (33-31.1N 078-58.1W) OR
CITY OF RICHMOND WRECK (30-01.8N 078-55.5W)
AND RETURN. VESSELS IN VICINITY REQUESTED
TO KEEP A SHARP LOOKOUT, ASSIST IF POSSIBLE.
REPORTS TO U.S. COAST GUARD MIAMI,
PHONE: 305 415 6800.
